data.description: This remarkable CBS home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, a 3-car garage AND an additional room ideal for an office or a 5th bedroom. Boasting over 2300 square feet of living space and a convenient open floor plan, the  property is ideally situated between Florida's Turnpike and I-95, near the vibrant Tradition area offering plenty of restaurants, bars, shopping, schools, and entertainment. The highlight of the backyard is an oversized pool and spa, nestled beneath a screened area, allowing you to indulge in relaxation and entertainment year-round. A well-maintained sprinkler system, supported by a well, keeps the meticulously landscaped grounds vibrant and lush while the fence surrounding the property offers privacy and a touch of sophistication. Make this beautiful place your home!
